<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THERE'S ROOM FOR ALL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lautha mangte hawldawk in, lam diklo a mangte,
 Gunchuh takin pui zelin, lam haksa leh neu ah;
 Amau di'n nunnem suoh in, Hukdampa Aw ngaiin,
 &quot;Kuong siemzawh eitai, hilh in, mitin di'n mun a um.&quot;

[V2]
 &quot;Mun a um....mitin di'n,
 Kuong siem zawh ei tai, hilh in;
 Mitin di'n mun a um.&quot;

[V3]
 2. Lungkhamna luiguomte leh, zan thim nuoia umte,
 Leh khawvak a umte chuh kipak leh lawp takin;
 Isu kawmah pui khawmin A aw nem chuh ngaiin,
 &quot;Kuong siemzawh eitai, hilh in, mitin di'n mun a um.&quot;

[V4]
 3. Lungsietna lungthim vawpin, Isu minin chieh in,
 Hinna leh hukdamna kim tu'n khawvel ah phuongin;
 Nisa um laiin kinin, kinin thim hung tun ma'n,
 &quot;Kuong siemzawh eitai, hilh in, mitin di'n mun a um.&quot;</lyrics>
<hymn_number>226</hymn_number>
</song>